It's been four days, with two appearing on the first day and one each day thereafter. 
On the first day, they were located next to the navel and on the scrotum;
On the second day, it was at the root of the thigh;
On the third day, it was at the chest;
Today, it is on the forearm.
There were no abnormalities before they appeared. After waking up in the morning, I felt a bit of pain in a certain area, and there was a small pustule there. It's not itchy, but a bit painful.
The specific shape is shown in the picture. One has been squeezed and probably not treated properly, so it got infected again, and one has not been squeezed.
Other information: The place where I live is dark and damp, with many mosquitoes; I have not had sexual intercourse recently!
Please give me some treatment advice. If another one appears tomorrow, I'm going to break down...

